com.epoch.physics

Class CanonicalizedUnit

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.epoch.physics.CanonicalizedUnit
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    CanonicalizedUnitConstants

    public class CanonicalizedUnit
extends Object
implements CanonicalizedUnitConstants
    Holds a unit reduced to SI units. (We use g instead of kg.)
